		"description": {
			"chat": "",
			"unidentified": "",
			"value": "\n      <div topic='Carpet of Flying' level='8'><p><b>Carpet of Flying:</b> This rug is able to fly through the air as if affected by an <i>overland flight</i> spell of unlimited duration. The size, carrying capacity, and speed of the different <i>carpets of flying</i> are shown on the table below. Beautifully and intricately made, each carpet has its own command word to activate it-if the device is within voice range, the command word activates it, whether the speaker is on the rug or not. The carpet is then controlled by spoken directions.</p><table width='100%' border='1' cellpadding='2' cellspacing='2' frame='VOID' rules='ROWS'>\n\n<tr maxcol='6' curcol='6'>\n<td><b>Size</b><br/></td> <td><b>Capacity</b><br/></td>\n<td><b>Speed</b><br/></td>\n<td><b>Weight</b><br/></td>\n<td><b>Market Price</b><br/></td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr maxcol='6' curcol='6'>\n<td>5 ft. by 5 ft.<br/></td>\n<td>200 lb.<br/></td>\n<td>40 ft.<br/></td>\n<td>8 lb.<br/></td>\n<td>20,000 gp<br/></td>\n\n</tr>\n<tr maxcol='6' curcol='6'>\n<td>5 ft. by 10 ft.<br/></td>\n<td>400 lb.<br/></td>\n<td>40 ft.<br/></td>\n<td>15 lb.<br/></td>\n<td>35,000 gp<br/></td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr maxcol='6' curcol='6'>\n<td>10 ft. by 10 ft.<br/></td>\n<td>800 lb.<br/></td>\n<td>40 ft.<br/></td>\n<td>10 lb.<br/></td>\n<td>60,000 gp<br/></td>\n\n</tr>\n</table><p>A <i>carpet of flying</i> can carry up to double its capacity, but doing so reduces its speed to 30 feet. It has average maneuverability, but a <i>carpet of flying</i> can still hover.</p><p>Moderate transmutation; CL 10th; Craft Wondrous Item, <i>overland flight</i>, <i>permanency</i>.</p>\n</div>\n    "
		},
